snippet.title: D no Shokutaku: Director's Cut - Live! 3DO Magazine Trailer
snippet.description:
As seen on the ninth issue of Live! 3DO Magazine from Japan, this is a preview for D no Shokutaku: Director's Cut, a Japan-exclusive updated version of the cult classic adventure game from the late Kenji Eno.

Developed and published by WARP
D: The Game, D no Shokutaku (C) Throwback Entertainment
